Package: climr
Type: Package
Title: Analyse and plot the latest global and hemispheric climate data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Andrew","Parnell", email = "andrew.parnell@ucd.ie", role =
    c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Downloads, analyses and plots the latest climate data from NASA at
    monthly, quarterly, and yearly time scales. Performs basic analysis on said data
    and creates nice plots.
License: GPL (>= 2)
LazyData: TRUE
Imports:
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    readr,
    magrittr,
    stats,
    ggplot2,
    tibble,
    viridis
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat
